original: Häge, Rolf Hugo Gerhard, läroverksadjunkt, Lidköping, f. 3/6/02 i Öja, Malmöh. 1. G. 41 m. Mary Persson. Barn: Inger f. 44, Kerstin 47. — Stud:ex. 21, fil. mag. 26 samt teol. stud. 27-28 i Lund, provår v. Gbgs folksk:sem. 31-32. Lär. v. Hultsfreds ensk. ilärov. 26, Hälsingb. gosslärov. 27, i Svalöv 28-29, Tranås 29, Ronneby 30, Kalmar 30-31 o. 32-35, ämneslär. v. Norrköp. komm. mellansk. 35-39, adj. i modersm. o. hist. m. samh:-, lära v. Lidköp. samrealsk. sed. 39.
translated: Häge, Rolf Hugo Gerhard, schoolteacher, Lidköping, b. 3/6/02 in Öja, Malmöh. 1st marriage in 1941 to Mary Persson. Children: Inger b. 1944, Kerstin b. 1947. - Studied: graduated from high school in 1921, Bachelor of Arts in 1926, and studied theology from 1927-28 in Lund, held a trainee year at the Gothenburg elementary school from 1931-32. Taught at Hultsfreds private high school in 1926, at Hälsingborg boys' high school in 1927, in Svalöv from 1928-1929, in Tranås in 1929, in Ronneby in 1930, in Kalmar from 1930-1931 and 1932-1935, and as a subject teacher at the Norrköping Municipal Middle School from 1935-1939. Has been a schoolteacher in the subjects mother tongue and history and social sciences at the Lidköpings Real School since 1939.
